## Status Colors

| Status | Color Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| Success / Active | `--color-success` | {{COLOR_SUCCESS}} | Completed, active, online |
| Warning / Pending | `--color-warning` | {{COLOR_WARNING}} | Needs attention, in progress |
| Error / Cancelled | `--color-destructive` | {{COLOR_DESTRUCTIVE}} | Failed, cancelled, overdue |
| Info / Draft | `--color-info` | {{COLOR_INFO}} | Informational, draft |
| Neutral / Inactive | `--color-muted` | {{COLOR_MUTED}} | Disabled, archived |

